# Biome Workflow

Use Biome as the single formatter/linter for all AI-generated edits.

- After substantive code edits, run `npm run format`.
- Then run `npm run lint`.
- If lint reports fixable issues, run `npm run lint:fix` and re-run `npm run lint`.
- Do not introduce ESLint or Prettier configs/scripts.
- Keep import ordering and formatting Biome-compliant before finishing.

For non-code edits (for example docs-only changes), skip command runs unless requested.
